{"slug":"sirkuler-25-0227eng","reference":"Sirkuler_25_0227ENG","gazette":"Department of Commerce","title":"Regarding the implementation of the Decision imposing additional duty on aluminum imports into the United States","date":"17 Mart 2025","bodyHtml":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 1rem; outline: 0px !important;\">In accordance with the US Presidential Decree No. 10895, an additional tax of 25% was imposed on aluminum imports into the U.S regardless of country.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 1rem; outline: 0px !important;\">The notification regarding the implementation of this Decision was also published.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 1rem; outline: 0px !important;\">As of March 12, 2025, an additional 25% duty was applied to all product groups.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Cabin, serif; font-size: 16px; outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-decoration-line: underline; outline: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://www.govinfo.gov/content/pkg/FR-2025-03-05/pdf/2025-03596.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--bs-link-color-rgb),var(--bs-link-opacity,1)); outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">Click here for the pdf version of the notification.</font></font></a><br style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Cabin, serif; font-size: 16px; outline: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://www.govinfo.gov/content/pkg/FR-2025-03-05/html/2025-03596.htm\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--bs-link-color-rgb),var(--bs-link-opacity,1)); text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inher